subHeadline: Travel excellence made simple and flexible
subText: Indochina Explorers management team consist of passionate & visionary people in an operating and representative network throughout Thailand, Vietnam, Denmark, Holland and Poland.

From our head office in Bangkok we have the agility, innovation and operation excellence to service a substantial set of professional clients in a broad palette of diverse consumer taste and preferences. By this, we reach the important organisation efficiency that release tremendous synergies.
We work and operate with People Skills: Human Values and Insights.
We design dynamic teams, pay great attention in details to advise and serve our clients on a personal level.
We use our experience, insights and competence to support our partners with rich content and value to offer any Explorer traveler the best sights and beyond.

pageTagline: Udforsk det charmerende og underfulde Sydøstasien
subText:
Sydøst asien var engang bedre kendt som Indokina, den spændende region som på mystisk vis forbinder Indien og Kina. 
Datidens rejsende beskev regionen som fuldt af mystik, forskellige farver og mangeartede oplevelser. 
I dag er denne del af verdenen måske mere divers end den nogenside har været. 

En verden pakket med et utal af oplevelser som venter på at opfylde din rejse-drøm
